{"tid":1655672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔揪出「假民主真建制」參選人 揭地區關注組成員力撐保皇黨","createTime":"2019-10-15T07:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T06:30:25.000Z","uid":189678,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2c58e680f2e9082e81402bf4f742b44dc291e78a","tid":1655672,"uid":189678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登仔做到嘢系列<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n新聞link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60155805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60155805&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9E2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=49eb65b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60155805&h=bab7cb90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60155805</a><br />\n<br />\n出哂新聞！大家各自搵返自己區嘅假獨立建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊齊扔俾隔離樓主做整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強大樓主的原post：<br />\n［有圖逐個捉］同我認住佢哋！假獨立真建制人士已現形<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655018</a><br />\n<br />\n有人餵埋俾你都唔食<br />\n咁都想要民主？<br />\n一齊做嘢啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im